---
title: American-Style Barbecue Chicken with Potato Wedges & Charred Corn Slaw
description: Eat the rainbow with this tasty mix of All-American flavours. Tender chicken gets a lightly spiced and saucy coating, with potato
wedges, charred corn and a creamy slaw to round out the meal. It's a taste of an American BBQ right in your own home!

